<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.2">
<l>iṉṟu muṟṟu mutuku nōva virunti ḻaittavic ciṟṟilai</l>
<l>naṉṟuṅ kaṇṇuṟa nōkki nāṅkoḷu mārvan taṉṉait taṇikiṭāy</l>
<l>aṉṟu pālaka ṉāki yālilai mēṟṟu yiṉṟavem mātiyāy</l>
<l>eṉṟu muṉṟaṉak keṅkaṇ mēlirak kameḻā tatem pāvamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look well fixing [your] eyes are fixed this sand house</l>
<l>that [we] built throughout the whole of today sitting down so that [our] backs hurt,</l>
<l rend="indent">and satisfy the desire that we have,</l>
<l>Our first Cause who slept on the banyan leaf, becoming a child on that day!</l>
<l>That You should never have felt compassion for us is indeed the result of our sins!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
